Detailed Description

This is a sub-structure in CSL_Aif2TmLinkSetup. This structure is used for configuring the parameters of the CPRI params relating to TM.

Uint16 CSL_Aif2CpriTmSetup::L1InbandEn

CPRI Link L1 Inband data 9 bits mask Bit 8: LOS_LOSERR_EN, Bit 7: LOS_LOSRX_EN, Bit 6: LOF_LOFERR_EN, Bit 5: LOF_LOFRX_EN, Bit 4: RAI_LOSERR_EN, Bit 3: RAI_LOSRX_EN, Bit 2: RAI_LOFERR_EN, Bit 1: RAI_LOFRX_EN, Bit 0: RAI_RAIRX_EN
